### CI/CD Integration

Add schema drift check to your CI pipeline:

```yaml
# .github/workflows/schema-check.yml
name: Schema Drift Check
on: [pull_request]

jobs:
  check-schema:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4
      - run: npm ci
